node.text: You don’t say ganja?
Bubble tea delivery sounds good right about now

To make your friends smile, why not send bubble tea their way? This is my third comic collaboration with @gongchasgofficial to spread kindness in these trying times❤️
-
You can get Gong Cha bubble tea from @professorbrawn which is fostering an inclusive workplace and employs people with special needs. Support them if you want to get your bubble tea fix!
-
Stay safe, stay strong, stay kind and stay #SGUnited!
#circuitbreaker #bubbletea #bubbletealover #nationalbubbleteaday #gongcha #igcomicfamily #igcomic #comicart #wholesome #stayhome #stayhomesg #stayhomewithsg #stayunited #corgilover
